<A>__{the thick fog blankets the entire bay now, and the town. the only structure visible is fort charles, high on the bluff, like a tall ship sailing a sea of grey. above the fort is a clear black sky sprinkled with stars. a waxing moon shines, giving both fort and fog an eerie glow. angle fort charles, just below the stone parapets of the fort, visible briefly deep in the fog, like a shark fin slicing through the water: the topmast of a ship, black sails billowing. flying from the mast is a flag with white aztec skull. the black pearl has come to port royal.}
